description: Located in the desirable Thomas Park neighborhood, this spacious 3 Family has architectural charm with beautiful crown moldings, skylight and hardwood floors throughout. Private decks off the back of each unit. Incredible investment opportunity in an area poised for continued growth with lots of new development and a very popular area! This property is ideally located, convenient to South Boston's renowned restaurants, beaches, Dorchester Heights, and the Seaport.  Sold AS IS.
